Class DSVisTwoResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.web.visualisation.definition.result.AbstractDSVisResult<AttrMapping,DSVisTwoSubresult>
      • org.pikater.web.visualisation.definition.result.DSVisTwoResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DSVisTwoSubresult>, ProgressDialog.IProgressDialogTaskResult

    public class DSVisTwoResult
extends AbstractDSVisResult<AttrMapping,DSVisTwoSubresult>

    This class represents the results generated by dataset comparison. In other words, a series of scatter plots that each compare certain column of the first dataset to a certain column of the second dataset.

    The columns being compared are determined by DatasetVisualizationValidation.areCompatible(AttrMapping, AttrMapping).
